{"tid":1979553,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗10警食消夜有人大打出手　1名男警長被捕","createTime":"2020-04-19T13:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T14:48:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"516a22f89234ac90a06ea5fff546496c6ff5a721","tid":1979553,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"元朗區警員涉嫌深宵內鬥！消息指，今日（19日）凌晨5時，約10名休班警員於元朗屏會路一間食肆「消夜」期間，各人為怕觸犯「禁聚令」分坐3枱，然而1名警長與1名警員發生口角，1名女警員上前勸交，疑遭該名警長以玻璃樽打傷頭部。據悉，該10名警員均屬天水圍分區警員，而受傷休班女警被送往博愛醫院治理，最新消息指，1名男警長被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，當時現場分別有4名警長和6名警員，全部隸屬天水圍分區軍裝巡邏小隊第3隊。事件發生後有人報警處理，當衝鋒隊人員及軍裝巡邏小隊到場後，涉事的一眾休班警員已離去。至於發生爭執2名警員加入警隊逾20年，而被打傷的女警則有8年「差齡」，暫未知爭執原因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，事件已通報天水圍分區指揮官及助理分區指揮官（行動），事件將會向元朗警區管理層匯報，案件情況，包括過程、原因等仍待進一步調查。"},{"pid":"b8f10d923d48efd5b8070e0afab3ff3a97b7ea41","tid":1979553,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff86c9ac2b4411bd25720aa2d7253865c27d17c","tid":1979553,"uid":201359,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3916e7daadffdd5d8ce1d5e6399d47937d6638","tid":1979553,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8f10d923d48efd5b8070e0afab3ff3a97b7ea41","tid":1979553,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hk